\begin_layout Standard
The set of all components belonging to the same area represents a 
\shape italic
family
\shape default
 of a given type All components residing in a given family have similar
 but 
\shape italic
mutually exclusive 
\shape default
behaviors: therefore 
\shape italic
any object can have only one component of a specific family type
\shape default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A component is identified by its 
\shape italic
type
\shape default
 which has to be unique globally, and resides in a specific 
\shape italic
family type
\shape default
.
\end_layout

